data.message:
Remember to vote for Sarah's "Going for the Gold with Uncle Ben's Rice" photo, one of the finalists in the Uncle Ben's Beginners contest. If she wins, Red Bird Christian School will receive a $30,000 donation. 
Please vote daily until November 13 at https://beginners.unclebens.com/SWilhite. Share with and encourage your friends to vote daily for this great opportunity to improve the nutritional facility for the students at RBCS.
